data.description: You'll love this stunning home at the end of a cul-de-sac on over a .41 of an acre in the desirable Lake Ridge subdivision! Plus a bonus three car garage with plenty of space for all your projects. Six year old roof, one year old hot water heater and all appliances stay. The cook will love the beautiful kitchen with granite countertops and custom cabinetry! Primary bedroom is located on the main level and the primary bathroom features a double vanity, jacuzzi tub, huge walk in tile shower with double shower heads and huge walk in closet- you must see! Finished lower level features an additional bedroom, family room, wet bar and safe room. The screened in patio overlooks oversized yard and is perfect for entertaining. This home is a must see on your list!! Come check it out today.
